_sText:
Cs_armory_z-mez_final1 is a re-make of a map I made about a year ago (never released).
_____
The map includes very realistic features of a real life armory along with ultra High Dynamic Range lighting (HDR). Most windows/surfaces in the map are bump mapped using env_cubemap.
_____
THANKS:
SpawnZlive - Mapping/Testing
Viper - Testing
Jack Bullet Proof J.B.P - Testing
_____
Special Notes:
This is my first map ever completed. I do not want you to "take it easy" on me, if you have some criticism, let me hear it.
Also, any comments you have are greatly appreaciated.
You can e-mail me with suggestions/questions/comments at: zachhousedoc1@aol.com
_____
Thank you.
